{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5a9f22ceb8","title":"致陈毅、菜裕电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"acfd590423","index":0,"year":1947,"month":9,"day":13,"articleId":"5a9f22ceb8"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"32aba35b2c","type":"paragraph","text":"致陈毅、菜裕电口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"5a9f22ceb8"},{"id":"42985cd20a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年9月13日）必须注意不打无准备无把握之仗，对五军、七十五师暂时不打很对。对停房应采取即解即补方针。仔获后有数天训练，开一个翻身会（吐苦水），即可补入部队。彭习野战军全靠厚房补充，即用此种方法，而战斗力很好。用此种方法，只要不打无把握之使，每战均有存获，即能保持兵员的经常状态[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致陈教、栗裕电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"5a9f22ceb8"}],"page":{"id":"caaec1913e","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"5a9f22ceb8","start":278,"end":278}}}},"__N_SSG":true}